name: Sleep Express
description:
You're on your way home and it's late. Try to reach your station in time.

Movement - WASD

Look - Mouse

This prototype is part of the game jam "Beansjam". It was developped in 48h although due to personal reasons I wasn't able to work on sunday. Still eager to take part at this great game jam so I still uploaded the project. 

The bench and coffee feature is not implemented and only the tutorial level made it into the game.
